OL,4, 
OL,5, Hello, welcome toCSix-Forty.GMy name is
OL,6,CRobert HamptonGand these pages are     
OL,7, coming to you from my top secret lair  
OL,8, (my flat) in Liverpool.                
OL,9, 
OL,10, I suppose the real question is "why?"  
OL,11, Well, as with most contributors to     
OL,12,CTeefax,Gthe answer is "why not?"       
OL,13, 
OL,14, As a child, I was fascinated by the    
OL,15, teletext system. When the family first 
OL,16, got a teletext set, I often got shouted
OL,17, at by my parents because I would call  
OL,18, up text pages while they were trying to
OL,19, watchCCoronationCStreet.               
OL,20, 
OL,21, On rare occasions when I had the TV to 
OL,22, myself, I browsed teletext for hours.  
