OL,4, 
OL,5, When I got an Acorn A3010 in 1993,     
OL,6, I was excited to see that it came with 
OL,7,CMode 7Gjust like the predecessor BBC   
OL,8, Micro computers did.                   
OL,9, 
OL,10, I quickly learned how to assemble      
OL,11, teletext pages to produce colourful    
OL,12, chunky graphics.                       
OL,13, 
OL,14, I even created a teletext "service" of 
OL,15, my own, calledCFabtextG(I really liked 
OL,16, the word "fab" for some reason). It had
OL,17, news, games and feature pages, some of 
OL,18, which were written by bemused friends  
OL,19, and family members.                    
OL,20, 
OL,21, Sadly the floppy disc on which Fabtext 
OL,22, was saved is long gone.                
