OL,4, 
OL,5, I was a regular teletext viewer right  
OL,6, through the 90s and early 00s. Sadly we
OL,7, then upgraded to SkyDigital, which by  
OL,8, then had dropped the old-school text   
OL,9, services from most channels.           
OL,10, 
OL,11, Our house did not have a good aerial so
OL,12, I couldn't even switch back to analogue
OL,13, for my Ceefax fix.                     
OL,14, 
OL,15, The closure of Teletext Ltd in 2009,   
OL,16, and then Ceefax in 2012, triggered a   
OL,17, wave of nostalgia in me. I was thrilled
OL,18, a few years later to learn aboutCTeefax
OL,19, and the community of teletext fans.    
OL,20, 
OL,21, Thanks to Peter Kwan who has trusted me
OL,22, with edit access to the Teefax repo. :)
