OL,4, 
OL,5, Sitting here now, putting together the 
OL,6, pages with some chunky graphics, takes 
OL,7, me right back to those days editing    
OL,8,CFabtext.GThe only difference is some   
OL,9, people might actually see this.        
OL,10, 
OL,11, Something I am working on is using     
OL,12, modern scripting techniques to produce 
OL,13, teletext. The blog on pageC642Gis an   
OL,14, example of this - it is generated from 
OL,15, my website automatically.              
OL,16, 
OL,17, Likewise theCSudokuGon pageC648Gwill be
OL,18, automatically generated to update the  
OL,19, puzzle on a daily basis.               
OL,20, 
OL,21, It's a fun way for me to experiment and
OL,22, sharpen my Python skills.              
